{"tid":2304950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普通話的語音就是「以北京語音為標準音」，特點是有「輕聲」和「兒化韻」","createTime":"2020-11-29T08:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T02:58:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c6072faaa736a24b28f41dd9af64248f2ff44535","tid":2304950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"一九五五年「全國文字改革會議」和「現代漢語規範問題學術會議」通過了普通話的定義：<br />\n<br />\n「以北京語音為標準音、以北京話為基礎方言、以典範的現代白話文著作為語法規範」這個標準， 包括了語音、詞彙、語法三方面。普通話的語音就是「以北京語音為標準音」；詞彙就是「以北京 話為基礎」；語法就是「以典範的現代白話文著作為語法規範」。那也說明普通話和其他地區方言 的差別就在於語音、詞彙和語法三方面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twghkhnmp.edu.hk/school_subject_mandarin/subject_mandarin.html?=subject_mandarin_selfstudy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twghkhnmp.edu.hk%2Fschool_subject_mandarin%2Fsubject_mandarin.html%3F%3Dsubject_mandarin_selfstudy.html&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=ee834926\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twghkhnmp.edu.hk/school_subject_mandarin/subject_mandarin.html?=subject_mandarin_selfstudy.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9cae4e3c379557c4118b3546b7f1c3e89e6d80d","tid":2304950,"uid":385945,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"302e40d9a09d5e3d6bdcaa6d1b0f2068ff4b0492","tid":2304950,"uid":53026,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"所以國語同普通話根本係兩種語言"},{"pid":"ad922adfce539936ad99c1effaec6f09c2907142","tid":2304950,"uid":249979,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:38:36.000Z","msg":"台灣國語最好聽"},{"pid":"4d1c8fda59f1605eb7160eb3e4f9d8f400218720","tid":2304950,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"302e40d9a09d5e3d6bdcaa6d1b0f2068ff4b0492","tid":2304950,"uid":53026,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"所以國語同普通話根本係兩種語言"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"你可以咁講<br />\